Kenneth Lonergan -LRB- born October 16 , 1962 -RRB- is an American playwright , screenwriter , and director .
He is best known for writing Gangs of New York -LRB- 2002 -RRB- and for writing and directing Manchester by the Sea -LRB- 2016 -RRB- .
He earned an Academy Award for Best Director nomination for Manchester by the Sea , and was nominated for an Academy Award for Best Original Screenplay for You Can Count on Me , Gangs of New York and Manchester by the Sea , winning the Oscar for the last at the 89th Academy Awards .
He also won the BAFTA Award for Best Original Screenplay for Manchester by the Sea at the 70th British Academy Film Awards .